==Inventory==
*[[Toxic blowpipe]] (to kill minions)
*[[Serpentine helm]] (to venom minions at start of kill)
*One-click [[teleport]] (such as [[Ectophial]] or [[teleport tab]]s/[[Teleport scrolls|scrolls]])
*[[Ecumenical key]] (Optional)
*Any necessary [[god items]]<ref name="God Items">Respective [[god items]] must be worn at all times prior to entering an area plagued with a god or gods' followers. The god item can be swapped or removed when entering the boss room since the boss is aggressive regardless.</ref>
*2-6 [[Stamina potion]]s or 4-5 [[Super energy potion]]s (2 Staminas for low level, short trips. Maxed accounts use 5 or 6.)
*8-16 [[Saradomin brew]]s or [[Sharks]] (Bring brews & super restores in a 3:1 ratio)
*6-12 [[Super restore]]s or [[Prayer potion]]s
*1-2 [[Divine bastion potion|Divine bastion potions]]
*[[Trollheim Teleport]]<ref name="Brews">Drop two [[Saradomin brew]]s upon teleporting, and use a [[Amulet of glory|Glory]] or the [[Castle Wars]] [[Grouping teleport]] to grab two more brews and another [[Trollheim Teleport]]. See the [[God Wars Dungeon#Teleport trick|drop trick]]. Or bring two [[Trollheim teleport (tablet)|Trollheim teleport tablets]] and revert the one you didn't use.</ref>
* (Optional) A stack of [[purple sweets]] to restore both run energy and some health.
